headline: Walgreens Could Be About to Make a Major Move That Has Investors Thrilled
summary: Until recently, many Walgreens Boots Alliance (NASDAQ: WBA) investors were desperately hungry for good news to boost the company's languishing stock price.  Despite the fairly minor price bump from the apparent buyout discussion news, the pharmacy chain operator's stock has largely been a big downer this year.
